text: Arsène Lupin contra Sherlock Holmes is a 1910 German silent drama movie directed by Viggo LarsenArsene Lupin Contra Sherlock HolmesBuck Rainey. Serials and Series: A World Filmography, 1912-1956 and stars Jessica Schwarz, Mark Waschke, and August Diehl. ==Actors== * Jessica Schwarz as Antonie "Tony" Buddenbrook * Mark Waschke as Thomas Buddenbrook * August Diehl as Christian Buddenbrook * Armin Mueller-Stahl as Consul Johann "Jean" Buddenbrook * Iris Berben as Elisabeth "Bethsy" Buddenbrook * Léa Bosco as Gerda Buddenbrook * Alexander Fehling as Morten Schwarzkopf * Justus von Dohnányi as Bendix Grünlich * Martin Feifel as Alois Permaneder * Nina Proll as Aline Puvogel ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:German movies Category:1910 movies Category:German drama movies Category:German silent movies
